2004-08-24 09:15  (jcgonz)
---------------------------------
index.php
- Solved another session issue.
- Actually I discovered that the history module and
- the access log registry are doing more or less the
- same thing. The only substantial difference is that
- the access log registry is built in the users module
- and it calculates the idle time. Those calcultations
- are shown within the user lists and within the user
- details.

